extendedInfo.description: We have put together the best collection of game play, trailer, and review videos of Temple Running. Check out the most recent news headlines about Temple Running also. There is no time to take subway to Sydney, fast run to temple to block up the Temple instead!It is a 100 levels of block game._______________________________________How to Play:- Change the block so that it can fit each other.. - There is no time limit, but each stage has target points to proceed to next stage._______________________________________Tips on Scoring:The more blocks you clear, the more score you will get.Features:- You can pause the game and resume later.
